extends layout.pug

block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div

      h1 My Portfolio

      p.lead.text-light
        | Using Node.js and Express I have created a site to show off some of my previous work. Below is a compilation of my JavaScript projects I have uploaded to GitHub. Regex, object-oriented programming, API's, asynchronous Code and real time form validation are some of the technologies and skills used within these projects. 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3

    each project in data
      .cell
        a(href=`projects/${project.id}`)
          h5 #{project.project_name}
          img.thumbnail(src=`/static/${project.image_urls[0]}`)
          br
          br
          br
          |


      
